<p>SPAIN</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>El Mundo</i> (<a href="https://www.elmundo.es/cultura/literatura/2024/05/01/6631d0befc6c83ee0d8b457d.html" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>El Pais</i> (<a href="https://english.elpais.com/culture/2024-05-01/paul-auster-a-life-in-in-images.html" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
