<p>BRAZIL</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Folha de São Paulo </i>(<a href="https://www1.folha.uol.com.br/ilustrada/2024/05/morre-paul-auster-estrela-literaria-americana-voz-de-nova-york-para-o-mundo.shtml" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
“He used to talk about the force of chance, fatalities and coincidences; also of failure and the shadow of impending disasters; of the life of a writer, of banal and extraordinary events, of the absence of a father figure and of New York . . . Everything with a clear style, enhanced by the suspense characteristic of detective novels and by the influences of other writers such as Franz Kafka, Edgar Allan Poe and Samuel Beckett.”</p>
<p>ARGENTINA</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>La Nación </i>(<a href="https://www.lanacion.com.ar/espectaculos/paul-auster-el-reconocido-escritor-estadounidense-murio-a-los-77-anos-nid01052024/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>Clarin </i>(<a href="https://www.clarin.com/cultura/murio-paul-auster-vez-queda-tiempo-feliz-reflexiones-dejo-escritor-ultima-visita-feria-libro_0_E6pUzLyLDF.html" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>INDIA</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Indian Express</i> (<a href="https://indianexpress.com/article/opinion/columns/obituaries-paul-auster-books-us-writer-9303495/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
“Auster does what an artist is supposed to—tell the story of a time through the story of people.”</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Frontline Magazine</i> / The Hindu (<a href="https://frontline.thehindu.com/news/paul-auster-1947-2024-tribute-narrator-of-a-noirish-new-york/article68128839.ece" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>SWITZERLAND</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Blick</i> (<a href="https://www.blick.ch/ausland/autor-der-new-york-trilogie-us-schriftsteller-paul-auster-gestorben-id19695329.html" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>Neue Zürcher Zeitung</i> (<a href="https://www.nzz.ch/feuilleton/nachruf-paul-auster-meister-der-vermischung-von-fiktion-und-realitaet-ld.1765175" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>ITALY</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>la Repubblica</i> (<a href="https://www.repubblica.it/cultura/2024/05/02/news/paul_auster_morto_scrittore_new_york-422805926/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>Corriere della Sera</i> (<a href="https://www.corriere.it/cultura/24_maggio_01/paul-auster-romani-imperdibili-ac8d4cbc-07a6-11ef-b671-01d7382ef0c6.shtml" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>24 Ore</i> (<a href="https://www.ilsole24ore.com/art/addio-paul-auster-scultore-caso-AF0eMmoD?refresh_ce=1" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>NETHERLANDS</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>De Telegraaf</i> (<a href="https://www.telegraaf.nl/entertainment/397348482/amerikaanse-romanschrijver-paul-auster-77-overleden" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>SWEDEN</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Dagens Nyheter</i> (<a href="https://www.dn.se/kultur/forfattaren-paul-auster-ar-dod/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>Göteborgs-Posten</i> (<a href="https://www.gp.se/kultur/kulturkronika/paul-auster-fick-min-varld-att-skalva-i-grunden.6378945a-be5f-4b5c-8c96-640e7be945a2" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
<p>JAPAN</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><i>Yomiuri Shimbun</i> (<a href="https://japannews.yomiuri.co.jp/society/obituaries/20240502-183610/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)<br />
<i>The Japan Times </i>(<a href="https://www.japantimes.co.jp/community/2010/05/22/general/the-bright-career-of-a-literary-shadow-hero/" class="external" target="_blank">LINK</a>)</p>
										
																				
																		
